Class ResultsProposalPopup

  • java.lang.Object
    • PopupDialog
      • org.modelio.api.ui.text.ResultsProposalPopup

  • public class ResultsProposalPopup
extends PopupDialog
    This class defines the popup of proposed results that appears when user uses the 'Ctrl+Space' shortcut and there are several valid results.
